{"title":"The Service Course helps cycling pros give back with limited-edition threads","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/07/16/the-service-course-helps-cycling-pros-give-back-with-limited-edition-threads/","date":1626449400000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>It’s one thing to look and feel great in a cycling kit. It’s something else, and even better, when that kit is doing something more than wicking sweat and cutting through the air.</p><p>European bike shop <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/03/20/zipp-service-course-silver-cockpit-brings-classic-looks-to-fight-matte-black-malaise/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The Service Course</a> has partnered with professional cyclists Mike Woods and Esteban Chaves to create a limited-edition run of cycling threads tied to the riders’ greatest philanthropic passions.</p><p>The apparel includes bespoke ride-apropos gear and casual clothing. The Service Course designs its products to fit each rider’s passion and style; what’s more, the company puts forward its commitment to causes that reach far beyond the realm of cycling.</p><h2>Woods Cardio Club</h2><p><span><iframe width=\"696\" height=\"392\" data-ezsrc=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/36GrpZZJw5I?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en-US&amp;autohide=2&amp;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation\"></iframe></span></p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112145/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_6.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112145/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_6.jpg\" alt=\"Michael Woods Cardio Club sweater\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112145/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_6.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112145/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_6-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112145/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_6-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112145/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_6-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112145/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_6-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112145/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_6-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112145/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_6-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112145/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_6-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb25 src ng ngcb25 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112145/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_6.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112145/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_6.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112145/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_6-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112145/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_6-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112145/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_6-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112145/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_6-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112145/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_6-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112145/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_6-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112145/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_6-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>Mike Woods is a Canadian pro known as the “Cardio Cowboy” for his grueling training regimen. Woods hopes that his run of apparel will help (1) fight climate change and (2) get more Canadian kids on bikes.</p><p>The collection includes men’s women’s training jerseys, a ’90s-inspired hoodie, and a commensurately ’90s dad cap emblazoned with the logo of Wood’s new unofficial fan club, dubbed the “Woods Cardio Club.”</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112151/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_9.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112151/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_9.jpg\" alt=\"The Service Course Woods Cardio Club dad hat\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112151/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_9.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112151/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_9-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112151/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_9-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112151/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_9-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112151/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_9-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112151/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_9-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112151/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_9-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112151/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_9-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb25 src ng ngcb25 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112151/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_9.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112151/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_9.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112151/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_9-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112151/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_9-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112151/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_9-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112151/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_9-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112151/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_9-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112151/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_9-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112151/MikeWoods_Andorra2021_9-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>“The Woods Cardio Club, the main idea behind it is a vehicle to inspire people. What I’m hoping it is, is just a commitment to climate and to cardio. If you’re buying the kit, if you’re buying the sweater, if you’re buying the hat, you’re showing that you love doing aerobic activity, whether it’s running, riding et cetera,” Woods said. “But also, the goal of this kit is a portion of the proceeds will go to offset the carbon footprint and help get kids on bikes in Canada.”</p><p>For every purchase from the collection, Woods and The Service Course will make a small contribution to HopOn Canada, a games-based program that teaches children about cycling safety, and Gold Standard, which backs projects that help the world move toward net-zero emissions.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112157/TSC_MikeWoods_SantaPellaia_31.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112157/TSC_MikeWoods_SantaPellaia_31.jpg\" alt=\"The Service Course cycling kit\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112157/TSC_MikeWoods_SantaPellaia_31.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112157/TSC_MikeWoods_SantaPellaia_31-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112157/TSC_MikeWoods_SantaPellaia_31-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112157/TSC_MikeWoods_SantaPellaia_31-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112157/TSC_MikeWoods_SantaPellaia_31-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112157/TSC_MikeWoods_SantaPellaia_31-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112157/TSC_MikeWoods_SantaPellaia_31-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112157/TSC_MikeWoods_SantaPellaia_31-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb25 src ng ngcb25 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112157/TSC_MikeWoods_SantaPellaia_31.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112157/TSC_MikeWoods_SantaPellaia_31.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112157/TSC_MikeWoods_SantaPellaia_31-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112157/TSC_MikeWoods_SantaPellaia_31-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112157/TSC_MikeWoods_SantaPellaia_31-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112157/TSC_MikeWoods_SantaPellaia_31-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112157/TSC_MikeWoods_SantaPellaia_31-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112157/TSC_MikeWoods_SantaPellaia_31-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/16112157/TSC_MikeWoods_SantaPellaia_31-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>If you want to feel even closer to Woods, you can also train with the new <a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/playlist/7IRxJe023euXUpm9qBAbdy\">Woods Cardio Club playlist on Spotify</a>, which includes 90s hip hop tracks that will keep your heart pumping.</p><h2>FUN Chaves Colorful Crocodile</h2><p><span><iframe width=\"696\" height=\"392\" data-ezsrc=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/AyP0kn4K9pg?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;shows